        "CLIENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，CLIENT节点代表所有前端入口。我注意到您提到了流式积分钱包，这个应该和CLIENT并列放在前端层吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CLIENT",
        "WALLET"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，WALLET是独立的组件，基于我们自定义的NIP-60实现。它和CLIENT之间是虚线连接，表示松耦合关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WALLET",
        "CLIENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把CLIENT和WALLET归入Frontend Layer子图，用虚线连接。接下来是API层吗？",
