      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，API Gateway Layer需要两个核心组件：API Server用Go+Gin实现，负责JWT和NIP-98认证；还有一个Content Middleware处理内容分发。",
